Name: Miracle Star Chest (Bound)
Description: Opening it will randomly grant one of the items inside, and the obtained item is bound.
Description$english: Opening it will randomly grant one of the items inside, and the obtained item is bound.
Description2$english: A reward box as beautiful as a starry sky, and equally precious in value. Although the contents are uncertain, they are guaranteed to be various treasures. Many adventurers hope to strike it rich by opening this treasure.
